Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.29,0:00:02.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人與人的邂逅充滿了神奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.89,0:00:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各種刑事案件更是謎題重重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.29,0:00:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能與你邂逅真是有緣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.29,0:00:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天是發生在浪花的60分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.10,0:00:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,案件 推理 充實的特別篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.10,0:00:13.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唯一看透真相的是一個外表看似小孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.30,0:00:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,智慧卻過於常人的 名偵探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.17,0:00:22.73,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.89,0:00:31.24,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我永遠注視著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.02,0:00:40.37,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何  我如此  三生有幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.03,0:00:46.96,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每見到水平線  便有莫名哀傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:48.12,0:00:56.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遠遠地回首 過去的自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.71,0:00:59.93,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限感傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.84,0:01:06.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的轉輪不停地旋轉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.97,0:01:13.20,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠深入思考的只有  Mystery
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.48,0:01:19.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  命中的良人就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.86,0:01:26.46,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.62,0:01:34.89,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我  一直守候你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是豐中市的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.71,0:01:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後這個是上周發生的枚方市的案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.11,0:01:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩件兇殺案都沒有目擊者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.41,0:01:47.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,案發現場也距離數十公里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:52.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在正在調查兩名受害者之間的關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.51,0:01:54.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還沒有發現共通點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩起案子只有一點相同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.71,0:02:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為兇器的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.51,0:02:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.81,0:02:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩人都是被刀刺穿外套口袋的錢包直刺心臟致死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.01,0:02:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這件事媒體得到消息了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.21,0:02:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有 錢包的事還沒有公開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.71,0:02:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.01,0:02:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二件兇殺案不是哪個笨蛋干的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,模仿性殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.81,0:02:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 應該是同一個犯人幹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.31,0:02:29.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.01,0:02:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是無差別殺人的話 會引起騷動的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.41,0:02:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠山 大家都不要輕舉妄動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.21,0:02:44.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.61,0:02:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浪花連續殺人事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.41,0:02:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡是天王寺動物園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.21,0:02:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個是大阪體育場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.81,0:03:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後這裡就是 通天閣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.51,0:03:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣 大阪是個好地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.11,0:03:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,景色真不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.91,0:03:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我覺得和東京鐵塔沒什麼區別
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.21,0:03:11.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.31,0:03:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別把這裡和那個無趣的紅鐵塔混為一談
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.41,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無論是這裡的通天閣還是周圍的新世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.01,0:03:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都匯聚了濃郁的大阪人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.51,0:03:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像感覺和東京的老城區一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.81,0:03:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來該吃飯了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.91,0:03:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.21,0:03:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會有人來接我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法 我去旁邊抽支煙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.11,0:03:35.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快告訴我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把我叫到大阪來的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.71,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 你那麼在意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定有什麼吧 真正的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.11,0:03:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.21,0:03:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這次真的是撇開公事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.21,0:03:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是一心想帶你們到大阪來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.11,0:03:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人嘛 不知道哪天就一命嗚呼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.31,0:03:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什 什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.21,0:04:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我做了個奇怪的夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.71,0:04:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.61,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正在追逐犯人的途中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.91,0:04:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反被犯人襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你死掉了的夢哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別隨便殺人好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.81,0:04:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,盡情享受大阪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.51,0:04:27.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.21,0:04:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是大阪府警局附屬東尻警署的阪田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常抱歉我來遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.01,0:04:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察先生怎麼來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.61,0:04:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老爸說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.01,0:04:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然毛利大叔到大阪來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要好好招待 所以就派了人來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.71,0:04:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老爸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.11,0:04:49.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是說好要見面的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.41,0:04:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總部長在開那個案件的會議抽不出身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.61,0:04:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.81,0:04:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 那台車準備好了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然 照平次你吩咐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.81,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,借來了東尻警署最炫的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.01,0:05:08.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那車該不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.31,0:05:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.41,0:05:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個果然不同凡響
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.21,0:05:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警車最棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算堵車別的車也會讓路的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.91,0:05:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼想去哪兒呢 乘客們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.11,0:05:24.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.01,0:05:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打算叫我們坐這種車遊覽大阪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.41,0:05:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.01,0:05:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可是珵亮的新車啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.31,0:05:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.51,0:05:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要鳴警笛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣速度會更快哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.21,0:05:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得像犯人被帶到警察局去一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.91,0:05:47.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.71,0:05:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,介意這個幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又沒做什麼壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.21,0:05:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,堂堂正正的坐著就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.11,0:05:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這才是正宗的烏冬面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.71,0:06:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,湯汁透明見底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.71,0:06:01.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.11,0:06:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然有點淡但是非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.71,0:06:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.81,0:06:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 平次 那個女孩是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是新的這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.91,0:06:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看上去像嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.81,0:06:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 我從東京來的只不過是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.21,0:06:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.31,0:06:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感到一陣寒氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼 接著去哪兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.81,0:06:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.21,0:06:44.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃過烏冬面之後是大阪特產
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.51,0:06:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.51,0:06:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好吃了這個章魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.41,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一次看到裡面放了那麼大的章魚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.21,0:06:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.41,0:07:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從剛剛開始就好像被誰盯著似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.61,0:07:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 別胡思亂想 快點吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.51,0:07:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一點都不能大意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.71,0:07:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小蘭姐姐你不是要減肥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵板燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.31,0:07:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛不在吃章魚燒前說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.31,0:07:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我熟悉的一家好吃的店已經過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,順序反了 這樣沒法按順序參觀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.51,0:07:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大阪很多都是單行道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有些地方要繞很大一個圈子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如這樣 我帶你們去附近我熟悉的那家店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.51,0:07:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了 附近有那麼好吃的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.61,0:07:39.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我先去給老媽打個電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.41,0:07:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 別忘了米飯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.11,0:07:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵板燒和飯一塊兒吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.41,0:07:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這很正常啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.91,0:07:49.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鐵板燒是一道菜嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在米飯上澆上醬汁別有一番風味哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.31,0:07:57.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大阪還真有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.91,0:07:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.01,0:08:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那裡是我朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.31,0:08:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你吧 叫工藤的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一直聽服部說起哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.31,0:08:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於你的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.31,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽服部說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用裝蒜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.21,0:08:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我已經全都知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.01,0:08:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.01,0:08:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.31,0:08:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在東京勾引服部的那個叫工藤的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.51,0:08:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 你是不是誤會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.11,0:08:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我告訴你一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.01,0:08:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和平次從小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.81,0:08:45.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是被鐵手銬銬在一塊永遠解不開的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.61,0:08:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要想對平次動歪念 就先過我這關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼是你啊 和葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.31,0:08:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在這裡幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.91,0:08:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這傢伙也太好笑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說的工藤是個男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.41,0:09:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是男的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.31,0:09:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後 那個工藤的女人就是這位大姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.11,0:09:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.71,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.71,0:09:12.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.51,0:09:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家說不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.11,0:09:16.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種事你也會害羞的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.11,0:09:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然這樣怎麼不叫那個工藤到這裡來呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.61,0:09:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 工藤不就在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.21,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有事不能來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.51,0:09:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說他了 說說你們吧 剛才的鐵手銬的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.61,0:09:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小時候 在我們家的閣樓裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.31,0:09:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和和葉發現了老爸以前用過的舊手銬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.91,0:09:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們就玩起了警察抓小偷的遊戲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.91,0:09:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果手銬解不開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.51,0:09:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是個很糗很無聊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.51,0:09:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不是無聊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候不管洗澡還是上廁所我都跟你一塊兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.01,0:09:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋 這種事怎麼講出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管洗澡還是上廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.71,0:10:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,換句話說是臭味相投的一對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.11,0:10:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我為了做為紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特地收集了那個手銬的碎片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.21,0:10:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還放到了護身符裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.11,0:10:13.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真噁心 你快把那個丟掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.41,0:10:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們是不是男女朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.91,0:10:20.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.11,0:10:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和平次只不過是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.61,0:10:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是一直照顧著平次的大姐一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.51,0:10:27.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得真好聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.71,0:10:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她爸爸是大阪警局刑警部長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.91,0:10:33.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我老爸是至交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.31,0:10:36.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們小時候就經常在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.31,0:10:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,偵探小子和青梅竹馬的警官的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.01,0:10:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不吉利的一對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼 我覺得很好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.11,0:10:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為 我作為平次的姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.51,0:10:56.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能讓平次被奇怪的東京女人勾引
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.71,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直在後面監視著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.81,0:11:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,監視 從哪裡開始啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.31,0:11:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從通天閣開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.61,0:11:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼做這種蠢事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.31,0:11:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs21}原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.51,0:11:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.21,0:11:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\a6\fs21}剛才的視線原來是這個女孩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讓人討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.41,0:11:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我擔心你嘛 你還這種態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.21,0:11:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,飽了飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.71,0:11:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.21,0:11:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察先生也應該一起吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.31,0:11:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不不 我只是負責招待各位而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接下來去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.71,0:11:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像只剩下大阪城了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.51,0:11:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼上來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.81,0:11:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什麼關係 就帶我一起嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.21,0:11:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.75,0:12:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 這個男人是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.95,0:12:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道 突然掉在發動機蓋上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.75,0:12:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是從這棟大樓的屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.45,0:12:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上面好像有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田先生 馬上聯絡警方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.25,0:12:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.95,0:12:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.55,0:12:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.85,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼請你說明一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.55,0:12:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,將屍體從屋頂往下扔的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.25,0:12:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是的 我剛剛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 被叫去屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.55,0:12:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 有個人打電話給這個大叔說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.65,0:12:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屋頂上有個奇怪的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.65,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他只不過是上去看看而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.55,0:12:57.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在這棟大廈的二樓開咖啡廳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.65,0:13:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是屍體為什麼會掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.15,0:13:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在屍體被繩子綁住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.05,0:13:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掛在了屋頂的欄杆外 用塑料布蓋住屍體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.05,0:13:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繩子的另一端固定在門把手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.85,0:13:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門一開繩子就鬆掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.35,0:13:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,屍體的死亡推測時間距現在整整一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.95,0:13:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說 昨天的這個時候有人將他殺害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.85,0:13:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後掛在了那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.05,0:13:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼會掉在警車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.75,0:13:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會掉在警車上只是一個偶然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.75,0:13:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說不定是為了做給誰看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.15,0:13:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做給誰看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.15,0:13:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,透過錢包刺進心臟的刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.85,0:13:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這怎麼看都跟那個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.85,0:13:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.95,0:13:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.25,0:13:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 車牌號我已經記下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.35,0:14:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來你快告訴我 服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.95,0:14:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才你說的那個案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連 連續殺人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.65,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才掉下來的那個男人是第三個受害者嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.65,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.75,0:14:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三個人都是被刀刺穿錢包後刺入心臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.95,0:14:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且是在脖子被什麼東西勒住致死之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.45,0:14:26.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會是劫財或是什麼恩怨糾紛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.05,0:14:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 沒那麼簡單
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.75,0:14:33.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個受害者長尾英敏是便利店店長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.65,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二個被害者西口多代是小酒屋老闆娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.75,0:14:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後 剛才掉下來的野安和人是出租車司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.35,0:14:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們都沒有金錢糾紛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.15,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這三個人之間到目前為止一點關聯都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.05,0:14:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.55,0:14:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖說出生 成長 就學的學校 工作地都是在大阪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.75,0:15:00.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是完全是不同的區域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.35,0:15:04.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次 有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.95,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被害者之間的共通點找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.65,0:15:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.45,0:15:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鄉司議員 請解釋一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.15,0:15:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.85,0:15:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大阪府議會議員鄉司宗太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.25,0:15:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六年前涉嫌貪污時候的帶子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.75,0:15:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘書做了擋箭牌辭職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.25,0:15:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後不了了之的案件吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得秘書的名字叫長尾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 長尾該不會是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.85,0:15:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人就是一開始被殺害的長尾英敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 這個之前不是看過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼現在又
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.85,0:15:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是 想讓你看的是司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.55,0:15:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.05,0:15:53.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這 這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.25,0:15:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是第三個受害者野安嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.25,0:16:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像直到四年前一直擔任鄉司議員的司機一職
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.65,0:16:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前任秘書和前任司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.25,0:16:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這麼看來鄉司議員多少跟這件案子有關啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.75,0:16:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因為如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.55,0:16:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我們署的前輩正趕去鄉司議員那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.35,0:16:18.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 鄉司議員討厭警察是出了名的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單是能見到他就已經不容易了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.15,0:16:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼阪田先生 我們也過去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.85,0:16:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種事交給警察吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.55,0:16:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.85,0:16:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你們的大阪之旅搞得一塌糊塗的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可以輕易放過他呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.35,0:16:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們跟和葉先到我家去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.35,0:16:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次 那個護身符你帶著吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.35,0:16:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帶著 別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.95,0:16:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼待會見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.55,0:16:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個護身符是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我給平次的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.55,0:16:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直保佑著平次的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.85,0:17:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說八道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.15,0:17:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒胡說呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.25,0:17:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上回忘帶護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次就在劍道比賽中受了重傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.25,0:17:09.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在這個世界上只有兩個的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.85,0:17:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,非常非常重要的護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛才不是說了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.25,0:17:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小時候和平次被手銬銬在一塊的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.55,0:17:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個手銬的碎片我也偷偷放進了平次的護身符裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反正跟你沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.95,0:17:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是 是哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.85,0:17:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,話說回來怎麼不見那個小鬼的蹤影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.55,0:17:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.35,0:17:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會不會去上廁所了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.05,0:17:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來不能再坐警車了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.45,0:17:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉 阪田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要寫警車損壞的報告書吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.95,0:17:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 我已經習慣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.45,0:17:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過怎麼回事啊 你的肚子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.95,0:17:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.95,0:18:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個小鬼挺有用處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.35,0:18:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是毛利先生不會擔心嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.85,0:18:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係 待會我會打電話的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.15,0:18:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 平次你說的那個可疑女人的住址和電話號碼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.55,0:18:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已經通過車牌號查到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.75,0:18:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字叫岡崎澄江 39歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.25,0:18:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去年離了婚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個人居住在這附近的西都公寓裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.65,0:18:27.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先到這裡去嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.75,0:18:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也好 那個大嬸似乎知道些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.15,0:18:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我打個電話看看她是否在家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天下午一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在心齋橋發生屍體墜落事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.65,0:18:46.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個事件中被確認死亡的是野安和人 41歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.75,0:18:48.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在警方正在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.55,0:18:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒了我吧 饒了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.75,0:18:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在兇手尚未明朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.15,0:18:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.55,0:19:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是岡崎家嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.65,0:19:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是大阪府警局附屬東尻警署的阪田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.85,0:19:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,警察先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.05,0:19:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點來這裡保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.05,0:19:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再這樣下去我也會被殺的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.85,0:19:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以前的事我都說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.55,0:19:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點到這裡來 快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.45,0:19:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之請您鎮靜一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.05,0:19:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我馬上就到 把房門鎖上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要讓任何人進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.35,0:19:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 西都公寓已經過了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.55,0:19:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼辦 御堂筋是佛堂街一路上都很堵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.55,0:19:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞回去要花很多時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.65,0:19:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣還是跑比較快 停下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.95,0:19:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.05,0:19:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.25,0:19:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.05,0:19:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.25,0:19:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是剛才給你打電話的警察的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.25,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開一下門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,門鎖居然是開著的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.35,0:20:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸 你在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.15,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是阪田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.85,0:20:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 岡崎女士不在家裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.45,0:20:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 屋裡空空的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.05,0:20:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能 我再三叮囑她不要出門的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.95,0:20:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大嬸有沒有聯絡過你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.45,0:20:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼可能聯絡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的電話號碼都沒有告訴她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.75,0:20:47.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.55,0:20:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之 快點過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.15,0:20:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我總覺得不太對勁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.85,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我剛過了御堂筋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.85,0:20:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有三四分鐘就到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.35,0:21:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下面傳來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.75,0:21:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,公共廁所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.35,0:21:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.35,0:21:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 已經死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.05,0:21:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個大嬸為什麼會到外面來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且又是用刀刺穿皮夾直刺心臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.95,0:21:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.75,0:21:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了什麼目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.75,0:21:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被害者是岡崎澄江 39歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.25,0:21:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,死因是被繩索之類勒住脖子窒息而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.45,0:21:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀子是在勒死後才刺入心臟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.15,0:21:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現屍體的時間是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.85,0:21:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田先生到這裡的三四分鐘前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.05,0:22:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這個打掃廁所的大叔發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.15,0:22:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是為什麼每次犯人都用刀刺穿皮夾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.65,0:22:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,明明告訴過這個大嬸不要出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.85,0:22:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還會在這裡發現她被殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在立刻到心齋橋來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.75,0:22:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你見見以前的老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.05,0:22:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下午一點零八分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.95,0:22:29.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到了沒有 下一個就是你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:31.15,0:22:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下午一點十分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.35,0:22:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個無疑是犯人打來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.15,0:22:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是說那個大嬸聽了第一條留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.15,0:22:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去了心齋橋的現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.05,0:22:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來之後聽到第二條留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.45,0:22:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就在房裡嚇得發抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.25,0:22:55.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是是什麼呢 以前的老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.95,0:22:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該是指到目前為止被殺害的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.55,0:23:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田警官 從總署來的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.05,0:23:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.95,0:23:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服部 很奇怪啊 這個電話留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.75,0:23:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哪裡奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.25,0:23:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錄在裡面的時間和內容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.15,0:23:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛開始叫她「來」的留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.15,0:23:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和第二條「看到沒有」的留言之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.35,0:23:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有短短兩分鐘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,犯人是不是一直在監視這個大嬸的一舉一動呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.85,0:23:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總覺得很奇怪 這四宗連續殺人案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.05,0:23:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感覺上在被犯人玩弄一樣有種不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.75,0:23:33.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不祥的預感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.25,0:23:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.25,0:23:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.75,0:23:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒什麼啦 別放在心上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 又想起之前做的那個不吉利的夢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.95,0:23:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次 接著去哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.25,0:24:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去鄉司議員的事務所怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.05,0:24:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.95,0:24:07.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.35,0:24:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說起來這件案子還真是棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.05,0:24:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既沒有目擊者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.75,0:24:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也找不到事件之間的關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.65,0:24:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而被害者的身份卻一下子就確定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.35,0:24:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.05,0:24:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭兩個案件在發現遺體後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.85,0:24:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不久受害者的名字就被新聞播報了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.85,0:24:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.75,0:24:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被刀刺穿的皮夾裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.75,0:24:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四個人都放了駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.85,0:24:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.35,0:24:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.95,0:24:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們四個人都沒有違規紀錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.85,0:24:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼嘛 原以為會跟車有關聯 又猜錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.05,0:24:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且這四人獲取駕照的年齡和地點都不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.05,0:24:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有岡崎一人不是在大阪而是在兵庫拿的駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.25,0:24:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶 幹嘛到那去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:02.05,0:25:05.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個地方是以集體住宿考駕照聞名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.45,0:25:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集體住宿考駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.85,0:25:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,集體住宿的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:08.75,0:25:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓你見見以前的老朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.55,0:25:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有老朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.95,0:25:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔 那邊的電話號碼知道嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.25,0:25:18.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.45,0:25:24.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 岡崎澄江和西口多代 在那時住一間房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.35,0:25:26.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.55,0:25:30.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 四個被害者之間的關係漸漸明朗起來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.75,0:25:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 你不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.85,0:25:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岡崎當時在那兒直接取得了駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.55,0:25:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,西口卻在三年後重新去考駕照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.95,0:25:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個時候駕駛技術很差 沒通過吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.65,0:25:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會吧 真的是這樣沒錯嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.75,0:25:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.75,0:25:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岡崎和西口之外還有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:56.95,0:25:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前的集體住宿時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:59.65,0:26:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第一個被害者長尾英敏以及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.15,0:26:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三個被害者野安和人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.55,0:26:10.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有大阪府議會議員鄉司宗太郎三人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.15,0:26:14.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們都住在同一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.35,0:26:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.05,0:26:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不僅如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.55,0:26:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個宿舍04AD9A3還有一個我們熟悉的男人的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:24.35,0:26:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,熟悉的名字 到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:28.55,0:26:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沼淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:30.45,0:26:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沼淵今一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.25,0:26:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沼淵今一郎 難道是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:35.75,0:26:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在逃逸中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.25,0:26:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強盜殺人犯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:41.85,0:26:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了 那時候的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.35,0:26:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 的確是沼淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.75,0:26:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外的五人長相和名字也都一致
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.85,0:26:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.95,0:26:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想 他們在那次集訓中都順利畢業了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.15,0:27:02.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而那時取得了駕照的卻只有岡崎一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.55,0:27:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定發生過什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.15,0:27:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前的那場集訓一定發生過什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:09.55,0:27:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎 謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.65,0:27:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,關於20年前的事現在培訓所的職員都不太清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.75,0:27:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:20.55,0:27:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過 一定會有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.75,0:27:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前的那個培訓所裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.85,0:27:28.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生過什麼事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:31.15,0:27:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了 就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.55,0:27:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前那六個人畢業的當天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:36.85,0:27:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,培訓所的一個教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:38.65,0:27:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為酒後駕駛而死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:40.85,0:27:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名字是稻場鐵次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:42.75,0:27:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,培訓所第一魔鬼教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:46.35,0:27:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種解釋怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:47.85,0:27:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,逃逸中的沼淵用完了身邊所有的錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:51.05,0:27:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,於是將以前的事件作為交換條件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:52.75,0:27:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向大阪府議會議員鄉司勒索被拒絕後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:57.05,0:28:00.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他就把以前合宿時的夥伴一個個殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:00.95,0:28:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想以此再度進行恐嚇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.15,0:28:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或者是 鄉司議員作為下屆國會議員的候補
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:06.35,0:28:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想銷毀以前的醜聞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:08.55,0:28:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就指使沼淵殺了以前的同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.95,0:28:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.55,0:28:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,長尾和野安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.15,0:28:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在辭去鄉司議員的秘書和司機之職的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.15,0:28:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽說拿了好多退休金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:22.45,0:28:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個議員大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.85,0:28:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果向他提起20年前教官的意外死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:26.25,0:28:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以及集體住宿的同伴的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:28.55,0:28:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算再怎麼討厭警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:30.55,0:28:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不得不開口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:31.85,0:28:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:38.65,0:28:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 你在這種地方幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:41.95,0:28:43.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突然就消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:43.65,0:28:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 我忘記打電話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.55,0:28:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次 好久不見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.55,0:28:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連府警總部的大瀧警官都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.65,0:28:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼會到這裡來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:52.85,0:28:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和葉拜託我做司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.35,0:29:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接到阪田先生的電話 我們來接戴眼鏡的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.65,0:29:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多管閒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:02.85,0:29:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每次都差遣警察幹這幹那的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:06.25,0:29:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐警車遊覽大阪的你 沒資格講我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:10.15,0:29:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.45,0:29:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就把這個孩子送到總部長的家吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:15.65,0:29:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走吧 小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.75,0:29:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要 我要跟平次哥哥在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:19.85,0:29:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下 大瀧叔叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:24.15,0:29:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這裡畢竟是大阪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.85,0:29:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,案子就交給我們 你別插手了 工藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:31.55,0:29:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就知道你會這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:33.25,0:29:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候一定會趁機溜出來插一手的對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:37.65,0:29:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法 這個先交給你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:41.15,0:29:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:42.45,0:29:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作為交換希望你今天就忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.85,0:29:48.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回家以後我會把事件的經過滴水不漏地講給你聽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:49.55,0:29:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.55,0:29:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 柯南 快點跟我走啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:57.35,0:29:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.95,0:30:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會再讓他在大阪胡作非為了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.95,0:30:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用性命做擔保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.25,0:30:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼待會見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:07.35,0:30:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在對誰說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.95,0:30:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過肚子還真餓啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:15.55,0:30:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,30分鐘後就可以到達寢屋川總部長的家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.05,0:30:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次的媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:21.55,0:30:24.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說晚飯要做河豚什錦火鍋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.35,0:30:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真讓人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:30.35,0:30:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是大瀧 什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:32.55,0:30:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在箕面的山裡發現了逃逸中的沼淵的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.85,0:30:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好 我馬上到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:39.05,0:30:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毛利先生 抱歉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.45,0:30:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,河豚什錦火鍋還要再忍耐一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:44.95,0:30:46.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要繞道去一個地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:02.35,0:31:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 我馬上讓手下送你們過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.35,0:31:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個沼淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:08.65,0:31:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是攜帶槍支逃逸的殺人犯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.35,0:31:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事態好像變得很嚴重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.95,0:31:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對吧 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:15.65,0:31:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.55,0:31:20.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼樣 情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:20.95,0:31:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大瀧警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.85,0:31:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們發現了被丟棄在空地上的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.65,0:31:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是沼淵本人還沒有找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.55,0:31:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那間小屋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.35,0:31:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才過去看過了 裡面沒有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:33.35,0:31:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,該不會棄車跑了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:36.45,0:31:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他在的 就在那裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:38.85,0:31:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟 你什麼時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:42.25,0:31:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來看看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:44.25,0:31:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我發現這個隱藏在草叢中的垃圾箱底部有些未燒盡的紙片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:49.75,0:31:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看 五天前和三天前便利店的收據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:54.15,0:31:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有保質期到今天為止的便利店便當的貼紙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:58.25,0:32:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天在這種地方吃便利店便當的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.85,0:32:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:03.15,0:32:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.25,0:32:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,通緝犯如果出現在便利店的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.05,0:32:10.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或許是別人幫他買的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:10.75,0:32:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人故意把他藏在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:13.45,0:32:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了某些目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:25.95,0:32:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到沼淵了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:28.05,0:32:28.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,情況怎樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:29.45,0:32:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有 有跡象表明這裡很久以前曾有人住過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:38.85,0:32:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,窗框上沾有泥土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.55,0:32:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有那邊的柱子和橫樑上沒有蜘蛛網
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:46.15,0:32:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對了 把腳踩在窗框上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:55.35,0:32:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.75,0:33:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從這裡好像可以進入閣樓哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.45,0:33:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等小弟弟 接下來交給我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:17.35,0:33:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沼淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.25,0:33:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沼淵今一郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:20.75,0:33:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以強盜殺人的嫌疑犯的名義將你逮捕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.95,0:33:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.55,0:33:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快點給我吃的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:29.95,0:33:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 鄉司大叔不見客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.45,0:33:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊 我們從傍晚就在這裡一直等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:37.95,0:33:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣只會浪費時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.15,0:33:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:40.85,0:33:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就看在前輩們的面子上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:42.85,0:33:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乖乖聽話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:45.35,0:33:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,議員 不能再讓警官們在外面等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:49.65,0:33:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他們去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.15,0:33:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過一會兒他們就會死心回去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:53.65,0:33:54.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:54.65,0:33:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把剛才打來的那個奇怪的電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:57.25,0:33:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告訴警官們怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:59.25,0:34:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:01.15,0:34:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個絕對不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:03.45,0:34:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一小時後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:04.55,0:34:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們以20年前的事件做個交易怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:08.75,0:34:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打開後門 在遠處的那個倉庫裡一個人等著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.25,0:34:16.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,絕對不能說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:17.65,0:34:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的 叫你不要亂跑的 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:22.25,0:34:24.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老是讓人擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.55,0:34:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 快點走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.05,0:34:37.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:39.35,0:34:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.35,0:34:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滾開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.05,0:34:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沼淵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:00.25,0:35:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:02.45,0:35:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 振作點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:04.45,0:35:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.65,0:35:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:15.65,0:35:17.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:17.55,0:35:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不不 沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:21.55,0:35:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田先生呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:23.05,0:35:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才他說要上廁所就出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.05,0:35:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼我也去一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:30.65,0:35:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,柯南 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:33.45,0:35:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們誰快點開車把他送到醫院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:36.05,0:35:36.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:38.35,0:35:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:39.25,0:35:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只不過有一點點痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:41.05,0:35:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,胡說 剛才刀明明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.65,0:35:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,護身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:52.05,0:35:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定是平次哥哥借給我的護身符救了我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:56.25,0:35:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.15,0:36:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們看 刀子一定是恰好刺入鐵圈中間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:00.85,0:36:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刀尖被卡住了才沒有能刺進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:06.25,0:36:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別再亂來了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:08.75,0:36:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你給我起來 快點走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:12.95,0:36:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個人為什麼 左手被銬了兩個手銬呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:16.25,0:36:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個嗎 不知道為什麼這傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:19.25,0:36:22.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,左手跟柱子銬在了一塊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:22.45,0:36:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法只能切斷那手銬的鏈子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:25.05,0:36:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後用我的手銬再銬上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:28.25,0:36:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被手銬銬著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:30.45,0:36:35.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像小弟弟你說的 有人在送東西給這傢伙吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:37.35,0:36:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.15,0:36:40.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說 難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:42.25,0:36:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:46.55,0:36:47.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.15,0:37:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你再怎麼等 鄉司那大叔都不會來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.65,0:37:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.05,0:37:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.15,0:37:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連續殺人事件的犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.65,0:37:17.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:18.45,0:37:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是對這個倉庫感到好奇進來看看罷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:24.15,0:37:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先是屍體墜落在警車上的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.75,0:37:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完美地按照計劃把我們帶到那裡去的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:31.25,0:37:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們從店裡出來的當口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:34.15,0:37:38.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打了手機 讓屍體自動掉下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:39.45,0:37:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啟動了這個你早就準備好的計劃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.35,0:37:45.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後在我們跑去屋頂的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.95,0:37:48.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用手機把岡崎女士叫到現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.35,0:37:53.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,預計到她出門後在她的電話裡錄下了恐嚇的留言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:53.95,0:37:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓她回家就嚇得躲在房裡不敢出門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:58.65,0:38:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,巧妙地讓我在現場目擊到她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:01.65,0:38:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令我加深了對她的印象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:04.05,0:38:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後你開車在即將到達她公寓的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:06.45,0:38:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟我提起此事 向她家打了電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:10.15,0:38:12.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後聽到她驚嚇得顫抖的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:13.35,0:38:15.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等我跳下車後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:16.05,0:38:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上把車停在小路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:18.15,0:38:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊追趕我一邊再次給她打電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:23.75,0:38:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是剛才打電話來的警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.45,0:38:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,待在家裡太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.85,0:38:28.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到旁邊的公共廁所裡等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.75,0:38:29.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:31.05,0:38:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後就在我進入她房間的同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:35.95,0:38:37.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就在廁所裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:38.85,0:38:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用繩子 把她給勒死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.95,0:38:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我們發現屍體後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:47.65,0:38:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立即就看到你開車抵達她公寓是因為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.45,0:38:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你借了兩輛從車身到車內一模一樣的車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.25,0:38:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在殺害她之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:56.75,0:39:00.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬上鑽進事先停在公寓旁的另一輛車裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:01.55,0:39:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,假裝因為單行道而不得不繞過御堂筋匆匆趕到的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.95,0:39:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自當起了我的司機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.75,0:39:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,故意把我帶到案發現場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:13.95,0:39:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是為了到這裡來 殺害鄉司那個傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:17.75,0:39:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對方是大阪府議會議員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:19.45,0:39:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一出門就會引人注目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.65,0:39:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,搞不好還會帶上貼身保鏢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:24.65,0:39:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果是跟我一起來到這裡的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:26.65,0:39:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算在房子周圍隨意走動也不會引起懷疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.45,0:39:34.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你從哪裡察覺的 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:35.45,0:39:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一開始是租來的車的反光鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:38.75,0:39:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二次乘的時候感覺和剛才的角度有些不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:42.65,0:39:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後看了傳真來的照片我突然發覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:46.25,0:39:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前死亡的教官和你長得很像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:52.05,0:39:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我進一步肯定自己的猜測是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:53.35,0:39:55.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到你駕車的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:55.45,0:39:59.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和野安還有岡崎一樣你也有調整後視鏡的習慣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:02.05,0:40:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個是同一個人教出來的證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:06.25,0:40:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道20年前到底發生了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.85,0:40:11.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去自首吧 阪田先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:14.35,0:40:15.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:18.15,0:40:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事已至此 已經回不了頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:21.85,0:40:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:22.85,0:40:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼 犯人是阪田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:26.25,0:40:29.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯 沼淵全招了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:29.85,0:40:31.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田想在完成連續殺人之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:31.85,0:40:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把罪行統統嫁禍到沼淵身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:33.95,0:40:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後讓世人覺得他是畏罪自殺 連沼淵一塊滅口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:38.25,0:40:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阪田在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:39.55,0:40:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個 從剛才就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:49.15,0:40:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子彈全打完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.15,0:40:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒法再做傻事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:57.75,0:40:59.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的腳中彈了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:00.55,0:41:02.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我沒事 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:03.05,0:41:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你快點走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:05.05,0:41:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.55,0:41:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的肚子好像也中了一槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:11.05,0:41:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我的父親
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.15,0:41:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20年前死去的教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.25,0:41:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是個對駕車相當嚴厲的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:18.85,0:41:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總是叮囑媽媽駕駛前一定要調整好後視鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:25.55,0:41:27.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的習慣肯定就是這樣形成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.15,0:41:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣的人怎麼可能會酒後駕車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.05,0:41:34.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我就當了警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.45,0:41:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了揭開爸爸之死的真相
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:39.35,0:41:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,解開這個謎團是在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:41.85,0:41:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在山裡的一間小屋緝捕到沼淵的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.35,0:41:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到和父親長得一模一樣的我時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:48.25,0:41:50.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那傢伙突然驚慌失措
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:50.25,0:41:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一五一十全講了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.75,0:41:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,饒了我吧 稻場教官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.95,0:41:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那天是我們玩笑開得過頭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:56.85,0:41:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,強迫你喝那麼多酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.75,0:42:00.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又讓你開了一輛剎車失靈的車子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:00.75,0:42:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,實在是因為你是魔鬼教官所以想看你嚇得發抖的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.05,0:42:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你就把參與那個計劃的六個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:09.55,0:42:10.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個一個給殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.25,0:42:13.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺人罪的時效是15年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:14.45,0:42:15.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.85,0:42:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有代替法律來懲罰那些傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:25.35,0:42:26.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:26.95,0:42:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把你牽連進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:29.15,0:42:31.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要說這些沒出息的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.05,0:42:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:34.95,0:42:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在日本唯一被允許佩帶槍支的警察啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:40.15,0:42:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼你不引以為豪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:44.65,0:42:46.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,站起來 阪田
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:46.95,0:42:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你警察手冊上的櫻花警徽正在哭泣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:06.95,0:43:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大瀧先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.45,0:43:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:09.75,0:43:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才被另一輛救護車送走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.85,0:43:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他真了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.15,0:43:19.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是他把你從大火中背出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:20.25,0:43:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:21.15,0:43:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.35,0:43:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是他想要取我的命嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:25.05,0:43:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:28.25,0:43:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他現在還是我的部下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.65,0:43:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你不要動手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:33.05,0:43:35.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遠 遠山警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:38.25,0:43:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鄉司先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:39.15,0:43:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們會再來拜訪您的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:41.95,0:43:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候來談談20年前的故事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:12.65,0:44:20.80,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想嘗試如履薄冰般危險的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.91,0:44:27.51,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望心中描繪的夢想能夠成型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:27.66,0:44:31.43,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.92,0:44:38.98,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙飛船如果降臨在自己面前 我一定會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:39.13,0:44:45.82,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋下朋友  離開地球展開旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.10,0:44:54.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說平靜的每一天就是幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:54.86,0:45:05.00,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我其實想逃  我害怕沒有你的每一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:05.16,0:45:13.60,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像如履薄冰般  偷偷地  戀愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:13.75,0:45:20.23,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心飛向你的速度比光速更快更遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:20.38,0:45:24.19,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Forever My Destiny
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:31.40,0:45:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次 振作一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:33.90,0:45:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:35.70,0:45:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服部的傷勢怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:38.40,0:45:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.70,0:45:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,總之得盡快將子彈取出來不然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.60,0:45:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,子 子彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:44.30,0:45:45.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阪田開的槍嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:46.50,0:45:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是他開的槍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:48.40,0:45:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想阻止他自殺不小心被射中的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:52.70,0:45:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:53.60,0:45:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼要做那麼危險的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:56.50,0:45:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我記得有個笨蛋說過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:59.30,0:46:01.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果用推理把犯人逼上絕境
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:02.00,0:46:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓他這麼死去就毫無意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:04.40,0:46:05.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,服部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:08.90,0:46:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行 好睏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:13.50,0:46:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓我睡一會兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:16.50,0:46:18.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以 不可以睡 平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:20.30,0:46:20.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:30.80,0:46:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:32.80,0:46:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,平～～～～～次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:39.00,0:46:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:40.20,0:46:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說了讓我睡會兒聽不懂嗎 大白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:43.50,0:46:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,痛痛痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:44.60,0:46:47.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看他這麼有精神應該沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:51.10,0:46:55.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我昨晚一直在想遊覽大阪的絕妙路線一晚沒睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:55.30,0:46:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以別在我耳邊發出那麼噁心的聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:46:58.10,0:46:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:03.00,0:47:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱歉了 發出噁心的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:09.80,0:47:11.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你碰哪裡啊 大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:11.90,0:47:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你才是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:13.20,0:47:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,誰讓你睡覺睡得那麼莫名其妙的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:15.40,0:47:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:17.70,0:47:19.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽著 我可是病人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:47:22.00,0:47:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來這傢伙沒那麼容易死
